Lemongrass aromatherapy candles are particularly useful for this purpose because the scent of lemongrass is known to have a calming effect on the mind and body.

In addition to their calming properties, lemongrass aromatherapy candles are also said to have antibacterial and anti-inflammatory effects, which can help improve respiratory function and promote relaxation.

To use a lemongrass aromatherapy candle, simply light the candle and let it burn for a few minutes to release the scent.
